@startuml
!define RECTANGLE class

RECTANGLE User
RECTANGLE CLI_Tool
RECTANGLE Scheduler
RECTANGLE ArticleCollector
RECTANGLE FeedParser
RECTANGLE WebScraper
RECTANGLE APIClient
RECTANGLE ArticleFilter
RECTANGLE NLPTagger
RECTANGLE Summarizer
RECTANGLE Aggregator
RECTANGLE ReportGenerator
RECTANGLE AsciiDocExporter
RECTANGLE Database
RECTANGLE FileStorage

User --> CLI_Tool : interacts
CLI_Tool --> Scheduler : triggers/manual run
Scheduler --> ArticleCollector : schedule jobs
ArticleCollector --> FeedParser : get RSS/Atom
ArticleCollector --> WebScraper : scrape sites
ArticleCollector --> APIClient : fetch via API
FeedParser --> Database : store articles
WebScraper --> Database : store articles
APIClient --> Database : store articles

Database --> ArticleFilter : provide articles
ArticleFilter --> NLPTagger : tag/categorize
NLPTagger --> Summarizer : pass filtered/tagged articles
Summarizer --> Aggregator : summarized articles
Aggregator --> ReportGenerator : weekly digest
ReportGenerator --> AsciiDocExporter : format as asciidoc
AsciiDocExporter --> FileStorage : save .adoc file

@enduml
